reviewText:
This game is currently (12/29/2015) filled with problems:
- obvious port from mobile, game mechanism does not suit PC gaming very much;
- FPS are not capped so I constantly got 500\600, consuming CPU usage for really no reason;
- there's a weird bug in the menu that randomly allows me to move the background instead of the levels page;
- gameplay is not very PC friendly and very boring too. Also no achievements, so it's hard to find the motivation to keep playing after a (very little) while;
- IT CRASHES TO DESKTOP EVERY 45 MINUTES SO EVEN IDLING IT IS A NIGHTMARE!
Got it in a bundle and I'm glad of that because I can't recommend it even at the -75% price.
